&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Overview /Objective:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The National Football League Digital Media Group is looking for an NGS Video Systems Operator that is highly motivated and able to work in a fast-paced environment. The role will require an individual with a flexible schedule that is punctual and dependable. He or she will be expected to operate, monitor, and configure software relative to digital video distribution.&amp;nbsp; This position is based in Inglewood, CA and does not offer relocation or remote work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
