&lt;li&gt;Document, escalate, and manage video distribution incidents to resolution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and update operational runbooks for live on air workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain documentation of video acquisition scheduling and live event programing.&lt;/li&gt;
