&lt;p&gt;The NFL digital video distribution business is growing rapidly every day, providing premium video and NFL game highlights to fans across the world. Are you ready to join the team responsible for creating and distributing NFL game highlights to multiple platforms and millions of fans? The Content Syndication Team is looking to hire a passionate self-starter to fill our open Content Syndication Coordinator position. The Content Syndication Coordinator, which is a full-time, seasonal contract role (40 hrs/week, 7-month contract), will work on a team that oversees the creation and distribution of NFL game highlights, VOD content syndication operations, supporting live streaming digital channels, application of metadata, and supporting VOD storage operations on behalf of the NFL Media content organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The team and responsibilities are both diverse and important and we are looking for a dependable and intelligent person who wants to get their foot in the door of sports media.&amp;nbsp; The ideal candidate for this position must have knowledge of NFL teams, players and current storylines and is also flexible to work early mornings, late nights, NFL game days and holidays.&lt;/p&gt;
