&lt;li&gt;Support programming operations for the “NFL Channel”, a 24/7 live linear stream available on FAST and CTV platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage titles, captions, metadata and programming of video content across NFL digital properties and our cloud storage system&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead in programming, syndication and delivery of digital video content to our partner organizations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Archive NFL digital video original and historical video content to our cloud storage system&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responsible for assisting in cutting VOD content from NFL Network shows and posting to NFL digital platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Limited oversight of projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Schedule-making duties for team&lt;/li&gt;
