&lt;p&gt;The NFL Films Camera Department’s Seasonal Equipment Prep Technician plays a crucial role in supporting the production team by preparing and organizing camera equipment used in filming NFL games, events, and documentaries. This position requires a strong attention to detail, excellent organizational skills, verbalizing technical needs, and to ensure that the camera equipment is in optimal condition for each shoot.&lt;/p&gt;
