&lt;li&gt;Strong organizational skills are needed in terms of organizing priorities, data, and time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Physical Demands&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
