&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reporting to the Sr. Manager of Media Management, the &lt;em&gt;Seasonal Media Management Specialist &lt;/em&gt;will be responsible for processing all incoming media.&amp;nbsp; It is the responsibility of the Media Management department, to protect, process, and deliver media assets to designated assignments.&amp;nbsp; This responsibility ensures the availability of all necessary assets for the edit and conform process at NFL Films.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Essential Functions&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
